      "file_path": "main/src/main/java/org/onap/policy/api/main/rest/provider/HealthCheckProvider.java",
      "patchset_number": 1,
      "line": 72,
      "message": "If a situation can exist where db connectivity is there, but the data(ToscaServiceTemplate for e.g.) is corrupted somehow, then I think this check makes more sense.",
